Sorry, my explanation could be misleading (I will correct it now) @springishere. If you try to use tensorboardX the model is exported with ONNX and then the same bug appears.

Answering your question, if you update to the latest ONNX and pytorch-nightly it should work. However, I don't know to which commit the fix belongs to. I hope that helps.
